Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午夜零点才能连接的诅咒网站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.60,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够登录的只有充满怨恨的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝点儿咖啡怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本圣良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把照片和底片给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以数一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺人总是引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩起来也不自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是全部了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个请您相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.20,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 听说过地狱少女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说可以帮人消除怨恨的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤人啊 那个态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 正好到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恨的人看来不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子 我会帮你消除怨恨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.40,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不知怎么觉得很怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么奇怪的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 很奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 又来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一边搞电脑一边吃东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没教养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱扔煮鸡蛋才没有教养吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子变坏的头等原因就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母的品行不端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那我们家就没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有这么棒的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过地狱少女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女 那个复仇代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 你的朋友里有谁知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有看到过那个地狱通信网站的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将它写成报道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 复仇代理人的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会热卖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱 少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有来啊 地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上网啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.90,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 用这玩艺儿查找东西方便多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天鸫似乎精神不大好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是心情有点不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也渐渐到了容易抵抗的年龄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道你工作很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也带她去次游乐场怎么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丫头会不会高兴呢
