Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨到想要杀死他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 那家伙的错祐子才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂也将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是死以后的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂将饱尝痛楚与苦难永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.90,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶 帮你留了点儿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧 要不胸部会长不大的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性骚扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父母心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在查啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有在查了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一去洗澡的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查过历史记录了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.70,0:13:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 既然你这么想查也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哦 我会小心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我点牛奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是汉堡店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.60,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不干了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来见店长的 他在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是田沼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.20,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 剩下的工资应该已经汇给你了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能出来一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有39的字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.10,0:14:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋 叫你待在家里还硬要我带你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 阿一看不见不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 带你去游乐场玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么把我叫到这种地方来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 木户她怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳啊 听说她跳楼的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看出来她这么烦恼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道原因了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是失恋什么的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你推下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了 我都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过分的诬赖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从祐子那里听说了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在账本上搞鬼 盗用了店里的钱款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子因为喜欢你 所以没有报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算来说服你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱全部还进去 就当什么也没发生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天在手机中跟我说的 之后就要去见你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子一直很喜欢你 可是你却
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 田沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有推她下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说谎了 我看见了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.00,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我非常担心就去那幢大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据什么无所谓 我看见了那就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你跟警察说也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我有不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女会帮我报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个在网上闹的沸沸扬扬的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴啊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西根本就不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.70,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在让阎魔爱替我消除怨恨之前  我只想知道一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那天的事情 你是怎么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不是事故 你根本没把祐子当回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜啊 祐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.40,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千惠 其实我以前就对你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个什么人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你是这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的友情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人 有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这里到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.00,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我好想见你 吾郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋 快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 一起摔下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.10,0:20:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 这次是两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.00,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛于思亦惩于念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 发生了什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 什么也没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.40,0:21:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也送你回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.00,0:22:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.90,0:22:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.20,0:22:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子 我以前也喜欢那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那时也可能是我变成你这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.80,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.90,0:22:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
